thread.title: Just Flo

author: Just Flo
title: Just Flo
text: I ordered 6 DIY signs for my out buildings; Wood Shop, Paint Booth, Tool Shed, Feed Room, The Barn and Whatever (a storage bldg for whatever is left over). 5 of the 6 are perfect! Easy to apply and look very nice. The one that is iffy is the one that says "Wood Shop" It actually looks like it says "Weed Shop." I'm going to have to replace that one because I'm a gal from the 60s and I can't have people thinking I have a shop for weed. LOL
